OL,3,CTrump to rebrand Pentagon as
OL,4,C'Department of War'
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump plans to
OL,7,Frebrand the Pentagon, which oversees
OL,8,Fthe US armed services, as the
OL,9,FDepartment of War, as he seeks to
OL,10,Fproject an image of American military
OL,11,Fmight.
OL,13,FThe defence arm of the US government
OL,14,Fwas know the Department of War between
OL,15,F1789 and 1947, before being rebranded
OL,16,Fto the Pentagon two years after the
OL,17,Fend of the Second World War.
