OL,3,CTrump to rebrand Pentagon as
OL,4,C'Department of War'
OL,6,FTrump is expected to sign an executive
OL,7,Forder on Friday to allow the Pentagon
OL,8,Fto use Department of War as a
OL,9,Fsecondary title.
OL,11,FHowever, the name can only officially
OL,12,Fand legally changed by an act of
OL,13,FCongress.
