OL,3,CTrump to rebrand Pentagon as
OL,4,C'Department of War'
OL,6,FTrump and US defence secretary Pete
OL,7,FHegseth have long talked about
OL,8,Fchanging the name.
OL,10,FHegseth even created a social media
OL,11,Fpoll on the topic in March.
OL,13,FHegseth posted "DEPARTMENT OF WAR" on
OL,14,Fsocial media after the executive order
OL,15,Fwas initially reported by Fox News.
OL,17,FIn August, Trump told reporters:
OL,18,F"Everybody likes that we had an
OL,19,Funbelievable history of victory when
OL,20,Fit was Department of War. Then we
OL,21,Fchanged it to Department of Defense."
