OL,3,CTrump to rebrand Pentagon as
OL,4,C'Department of War'
OL,6,FWhen confronted with the possibility
OL,7,Fthat making the name change would
OL,8,Frequire an act of Congress, Trump told
OL,9,Freporters that "we're just going to do
OL,10,Fit".
OL,12,F"I'm sure Congress will go along if we
OL,13,Fneed that," he added.
OL,15,FThe move is just the latest in a long
OL,16,Fline of cultural changes Hegseth has
OL,17,Fmade to the Pentagon since taking
OL,18,Foffice at the beginning of the year.
