OL,3,CTrump to rebrand Pentagon as
OL,4,C'Department of War'
OL,6,FHegseth pushed hard to eliminate what
OL,7,Fhe see as the impact of "woke culture"
OL,8,Fon the military by ending diversity
OL,9,Fprogrammes, removing of books in the
OL,10,Fmilitary academies, including titles
OL,11,Fon the Holocaust and a Maya Angelou
OL,12,Fmemoir and scrubbing off thousands of
OL,13,Fwebsites honouring contributions by
OL,14,Fwomen and minority groups.
OL,16,FHegseth has also presided over the
OL,17,Fremoval of all transgender troops from
OL,18,Fthe military following an executive
OL,19,Forder from Trump through a process
OL,20,Fthat some have described as
OL,21,F"dehumanising" or "open cruelty."
